s%20Oracle%2C%20Abu%20Dhabi%20investment%20firm%20MGX%2C%20and%20private-equity%20firm%20Silver%20Lake%20are%20all%20coming%20on%20as%20managing%20investors%20in%20the%20US%20spin-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20much%20influence%20will%20these%20investors%20have%20over%20the%20money-making%20side%20of%20the%20business%3F%20Not%20much%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20memo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-reaches-deal-with-investors-on-its-us-business-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETikTok%20CEO%20Shou%20Chew%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20to%20employees%20on%20Thursday%2C%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20investors%20will%20focus%20on%20national%20security-related%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20data%20management%20and%20algorithm%20training%2C%20while%20TikTok's%20current%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20will%20remain%20in%20charge%20of%20key%20business%20lines%2C%20including%20e-commerce%20and%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20Chew%20told%20staff%20about%20the%20arrangement%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20US%20joint%20venture%2C%20built%20on%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20current%20TikTok%20US%20Data%20Security%20(USDS)%20organization%2C%20will%20operate%20as%20an%20independent%20entity%20with%20authority%20over%20US%20data%20protection%2C%20algorithm%20security%2C%20content%20moderation%20and%20software%20assurance%2C%20while%20TikTok%20global's%20US%20entities%20will%20manage%20global%20product%20interoperability%20and%20certain%20commercial%20activities%2C%20including%20e-commerce%2C%20advertising%2C%20and%20marketing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20laid%20out%20by%20Chew%2C%20TikTok's%20new%20investors%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20on%20core%20business%20lines%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-shop-crossed-500-million-in-us-sales-black-friday-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5