E%3Cfigcaption%3EIowa%2080%20has%20900%20parking%20spots%20for%20semis.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20told%20me%20that%20just%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fari-legacy-sleepers-custom-sleeper-cabs-long-haul-truck-drivers-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20some%20sleep%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20a%20parking%20spot%20at%20the%20most%20common%20truck%20stops%2C%20like%20TA%20and%20Pilot%2C%20but%20after%207%20p.m.%20or%208%20p.m.%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20find%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20you'll%20sometimes%20see%20rigs%20pulled%20over%20on%20the%20shoulder%20of%20a%20highway%20onramp%20to%20sleep%2C%20which%20can%20be%20unsafe%20if%20there's%20heavy%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20hundreds%20of%20trucks%20settled%20in%20by%20the%20time%20we%20left%20at%205%20p.m.%2C%20the%20lot%20was%20nowhere%20near%20full.%20I%20can%20see%20why%20this%20is%20an%20important%20feature%20for%20tired%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESpeaking%20to%20truckers%2C%20I%20found%20a%20new%20respect%20for%20what%20they%20endure%20on%20the%20road.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221798%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lisa%20Otto%2C%20Truck%20Driver%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6944611604eda4732f2dd106%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELisa%20Otto%20is%20one%20of%20just%209%25%20of%20long-haul%20truckers%20who%20are%20women.%20She%20told%20me%20she%20can%20drive%20circles%20around%20the%20men.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Wyatt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrucking%20is%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20businesses%20out%20there%2C%20with%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20turnover%20rates%20in%20the%20US.%20For%20every%20driver%20that%20enters%20the%20industry%2C%20one%20leaves%20or%20switches%20companies.%20The%20Owner-Operator%20Independent%20Drivers%20Association%20(OOIDA)%20told%20me%20that%20this%20is%20because%20wages%20are%20low%2C%20drivers%20can't%20get%20paid%20overtime%2C%20and%20hours%20are%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Otto%20has%20over%2020%20years%2C%2048%20states%2C%20and%203%20million%20miles%20under%20her%20belt.%20Over%20seven%20days%2C%20she%20can%20easily%20clock%20in%2070%20hours%20of%20driving.%20She%20lives%20out%20of%20her%20truck%2C%20which%20she%20bought%20for%20%24230%2C000%2C%20for%20weeks%20at%20a%20time.%20She%20doesn't%20have%20a%20toilet%20or%20shower%20in%20her%20rig.%20But%20she%20does%20have%20her%20two%20weiner%20dogs%2C%20Clarice%20and%20Phoebe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20worried%20for%20Lisa%20being%20away%20from%20her%20family%20and%20home%20for%20weeks%20at%20a%20time.%20But%20she%20told%20me%20she%20enjoys%20traveling%20for%20a%20living%2C%20and%20she's%20so%20introverted%2C%20she%20likes%20her%20alone%20time.%20She%20said%20she%20sleeps%20better%20in%20the%20foam%20mattress%20in%20her%20truck%20than%20at%20home.%20And%20she%20reminded%20me%20there's%20FaceTime%20to%20talk%20to%20her%20grown%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20on%20the%20road%2C%20her%20dogs%20keep%20her%20company.%20She%20says%20she%20wouldn't%20know%20how%20to%20survive%20without%20them.%20When%20she's%20alone%20in%20her%20rig%20at%20night%2C%20she%20feels%20protected%20with%20them%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPreston%20Smith%20is%20a%20new%20driver%2C%20and%20the%20story%20of%20how%20he%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20business%20had%20me%20in%20tears.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222522%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preston%20Smith%2C%20truck%20driver%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69446160832e0ef1ead68328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPreston%20Smith%20got%20his%20commercial%20driver's%20license%20just%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Wyatt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20used%20to%20be%20a%20merchandiser%20for%20The%20Coca-Cola%20Company.%20But%20in%202020%2C%20he%20was%20shot%2010%20times%20in%20the%20leg%20as%20an%20innocent%20bystander%20at%20a%20club.%20He%20died%20briefly%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Doctors%20had%20to%20amputate%20his%20left%20leg%20to%20save%20his%20life.%20When%20he%20woke%20up%2C%20long-haul%20trucking%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20things%20he%20could%20do%20that%20wasn't%20on%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20moved%20by%20his%20story%20that%20I%20asked%20how%20he%20managed%20to%20stay%20motivated%20during%20such%20a%20tough%20time.%20He%20credited%20his%20family%20and%20his%20co-driver%2C%20Latoya%20%26quot%3BBlu%26quot%3B%20Howard.%20They%20run%20together%2C%20meaning%20they%20drive%2012-hour%20shifts%2C%20all%20day%20and%20night.%20One%20sleeps%20while%20the%20other%20drives.%20They%20only%20stop%20for%20meals%20and%20emergency%20bathroom%20breaks.%20If%20it's%20not%20an%20emergency%2C%20they%20pee%20in%20what%20looked%20to%20be%20an%20old%20plastic%20nut%20container.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20told%20me%20Howard%20gives%20him%20advice%20and%20helps%20keep%20his%20mind%20focused%20when%20he%20gets%20sad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELatoya%20%26quot%3BBlu%26quot%3B%20Howard%20deals%20with%20her%20own%20demons%20on%20the%20road.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222224%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Latoya%20Blu%20Howard%20Truck%20Driver%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6944628404eda4732f2dd145%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221562%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20keeps%20this%20plushie%20Hulk%2C%20her%20son's%20favorite%2C%20on%20her%20windshield%20to%20remind%20her%20of%20her%20son.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Wyatt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHoward%20lost%20her%20son%20nine%20years%20ago.%20He%20was%20accidentally%20shot%20by%20a%20friend%20when%20he%20was%2017.%20She%20says%20she%20feels%20her%20son%20out%20on%20the%20road.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20when%20driving%20throu