roadcast%20Tuesday%2C%20Dec.%2029%20(9%3A00-11%3A00%20PM%2C%20ET%2FPT)%20on%20the%20CBS%20Television%20Network.%20Pictured%20L-R%3A%20Rita%20Moreno%2C%20George%20Lucas%2C%20Carole%20Kin%2C%20First%20Lady%20Michelle%20Obama%2C%20and%20President%20Barack%20Obama%3Cp%3EJohn%20Paul%20Filo%2FCBS%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyonc%C3%A9%20brought%20the%20Kennedy%20Center%20to%20its%20feet%20with%20a%20fiery%20tribute%20to%20Tina%20Turner%20in%202005%2C%20and%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20shed%20tears%20while%20watching%20Aretha%20Franklin%20perform%20%26quot%3BNatural%20Woman%26quot%3B%20to%20honor%20Carole%20King%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20implemented%20sweeping%20changes%20to%20the%20Kennedy%20Center%2C%20encompassing%20the%20board%20of%20trustees%20and%20the%20design%20of%20the%20medallions.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%20presidential%20box%20at%20the%20Kennedy%20Center.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694578e864858d02d21724d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20-%20MARCH%2017%3A%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20looks%20down%20from%20the%20Presidential%20Box%20in%20the%20Opera%20House%20at%20the%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Center%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts%20as%20he%20participates%20in%20a%20guided%20tour%20and%20leads%20a%20board%20meeting%20on%20March%2017%2C%202025%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20After%20shunning%20the%20annual%20Kennedy%20Center%20Honors%20during%20his%20first%20term%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20fired%20the%20center's%20president%2C%20removed%20the%20bipartisan%20board%20of%20Biden%20appointees%2C%20and%20named%20himself%20Chairman%20of%20the%20storied%20music%2C%20theater%2C%20and%20dance%20institution.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20Kennedy%20Center%20Honors%20during%20his%20first%20term%2C%20but%20has%20taken%20a%20much%20more%20active%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20institution%20in%20his%20second%20non-consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20office%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20fired%20the%20president%20and%20Biden-appointed%20members%20of%20the%20Kennedy%20Center's%20board%20of%20trustees%2C%20replacing%20them%20with%20allies%20and%20members%20of%20his%20administration.%20The%20board%20went%20on%20to%20elect%20Trump%20as%20its%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20visiting%20the%20performance%20venue%20in%20March%2C%20Trump%20told%20board%20members%20that%20the%20building%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bbad%20shape%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20planned%20to%20renovate%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20changes%2C%20including%20the%20seats%2C%20the%20d%C3%A9cor%2C%20pretty%20much%20everything%20needs%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%202025%20Kennedy%20Center%20Honors%2C%20held%20on%20December%207%2C%20honorees%20received%20newly%20designed%20medallions%20from%20Tiffany%2C%20featuring%20blue%20ribbons%20instead%20of%20the%20traditional%20rainbow%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20occurred%20in%20December%2C%20when%20the%20Trump-appointed%20board%20of%20trustees%20voted%20to%20rename%20the%20center%20the%20Trump%20Kennedy%20Center.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Kennedy%20Center%20renamed%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20name.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69457f8f64858d02d21725f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20-%20DECEMBER%2019%3A%20Workers%20adjust%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BJohn%20F.%20Kennedy%20Memorial%20Center%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts%26quot%3B%20on%20December%2019%2C%202025%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20The%20Kennedy%20Center%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20voted%20in%20what%20they%20say%20was%20a%20unanimous%20decision%20to%20rename%20the%20facility%20%26quot%3BThe%20Donald%20J.%20Trump%20and%20The%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Memorial%20Center%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts%26quot%3B.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Diehl%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20White%20House%20announced%20that%20the%20board%20had%20%26quot%3Bunanimously%26quot%3B%20voted%20to%20change%20the%20name%20from%20the%20Kennedy%20Center%20to%20the%20Trump%20Kennedy%20Center%2C%20and%20the%20website%20was%20updated%20to%20reflect%20the%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20name%20was%20added%20to%20the%20building's%20signage%20on%20Friday%2C%20reading%20%26quot%3BThe%20Donald%20J.%20Trump%20and%20The%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Memorial%20Center%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20unanimous%20vote%20recognizes%20that%20the%20current%20Chairman%20saved%20the%20institution%20from%20financial%20ruin%20and%20physical%20destruction%2C%26quot%3B%20Roma%20Daravi%2C%20the%20center's%20vice%20president%20of%20public%20relations%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Trump%20Kennedy%20Center%20reflects%20the%20unequivocal%20bipartisan%20support%20for%20America's%20cultural%20center%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bhonored%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Kennedy%20family%20criticized%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20grandson%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-jack-kennedy-schlossberg-jfk-grandson-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJack%20Schlossberg%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0contested%20the%20White%20House's%20claim%20of%20a%20unanimous%20vote%2C%20writing%20on%20X%20that%20%26quot%3Bmicrophones%20were%20muted%20and%20the