%3ESukhwinder%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20yield%20per%20acre%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower%20compared%20to%20conventional%20seeds%2C%20the%20overall%20benefits%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326709%2Fcultyvate-agri-tech-solution-helps-paddy-farmers-reduce-water-waste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduced%20input%20costs%20and%20improved%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20far%20outweigh%20any%20minor%20differences%20in%20productivity.%20Besides%2C%20I%20am%20earning%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20instead%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20rates%20for%20regular%20wheat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Sukhwinder%2C%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20thanks%20to%20Aishwarya%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%2C%20who%20are%20promoting%20innovative%20and%20eco-friendly%20farming%20methods%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20food%20we%20eat%20daily%20nutritious%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20completing%20higher%20studies%20and%20gaining%20entrepreneurship%20training%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Prateek%20felt%20a%20strong%20calling%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20in%20his%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20advised%20to%20venture%20into%20more%20developed%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat%20for%20ease%20of%20business%2C%20he%20strived%20to%20focus%20on%20central%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20regions%20that%20still%20required%20substantial%20advancement%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%20the%20corporate%20world%20for%20a%20year%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20his%20ancestral%20village%20in%20Sitapur%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Aishwarya%2C%20who%20is%20an%20alumna